Freudian people,

00:10:37.592 --> 00:10:41.659
is that you are egoistical!

00:10:44.407 --> 00:10:49.491
They have such funny ideas from the yarn
of Mr. Freud

00:10:49.692 --> 00:10:54.666
that no sensible man would accept.

00:10:55.872 --> 00:11:01.593
