00:11:25.372 --> 00:11:31.447
you must get hold of books and find out,
where are we?

00:11:31.648 --> 00:11:36.000
I worked very hard in France, you know
that very well.

00:11:36.201 --> 00:11:39.251
I used to think, this is the gate of hell.

00:11:39.452 --> 00:11:43.215
But it is much worse than that,

00:11:43.416 --> 00:11:48.487
