00:12:21.060 --> 00:12:23.862
which was not fixed properly and made
to fly.

00:12:24.063 --> 00:12:27.349
What will happen to the aeroplane?

00:12:27.550 --> 00:12:33.851
If the children are given liberty without
the right sense of their duty

00:12:34.052 --> 00:12:38.793
