we have tried.

00:18:41.196 --> 00:18:44.305
Of course, one person is living
for the last seven years,

00:18:44.543 --> 00:18:49.950
but still he has no faith in himself.

00:18:50.151 --> 00:18:55.456
Maybe next generation might be better on,
if they come back.

00:18:55.657 --> 00:18:59.825
But as far as this generation is concerned,

00:19:00.026 --> 00:19:04.781
you should know your responsibility
is very great.

00:19:04.982 --> 00:19:09.725
All the Sahaja Yogis must take a vow

00:19:09.926 --> 00:19:14.762
that they'll fight this society and try
to save their country

00:19:14.963 --> 00:19:20.528
and their countrymen from a complete
disaster.

00:19:20.729 --> 00:19:24.097
There is going to be no war,

00:19:24.298 --> 00:19:29.365
only they will fight themselves and die.

00:19:31.341 --> 00:19:33.622
It's a very serious matter.

00:19:33.823 --> 00:19:39.199
For that, we decided to have this puja
of Durga today

00:19:39.400 --> 00:19:43.668
that all negativity should be destroyed.

00:19:43.869 --> 00:19:50.875
So many Deities build up the body of Kali.

00:19:51.076 --> 00:19:56.592
Every part of Her body was created
by a Deity, looked after by a Deity,

00:19:56.793 --> 00:20:04.577
and is also, later on, is reflected
in you all.

00:20:06.771 --> 00:20:10.845
So they say that God has made human beings
in His own image,

00:20:11.046 --> 00:20:14.667
I would say, I've made you in My own
image,

00:20:14.868 --> 00:20:19.781
all the Deities at your disposal.

00:20:19.982 --> 00:20:24.279
They're all with you, and they have created
you - if you see it minutely -

00:20:24.480 --> 00:20:29.769
it is the Deities who have brought forth
all the beauty that you had.

00:20:29.970 --> 00:20:39.568
They have made all this beautiful
congregation, beautiful transformation,

00:20:39.769 --> 00:20:47.424
and they have created such angelic people
out of you.

00:20:48.100 --> 00:20:50.696
They are always working it out,

00:20:50.897 --> 00:20:56.370
but one thing you have to do is to have
the drive.

